---
// UeberMichSection.astro — Terminal-Codeblock + Persönlicher Text + 3 Stats
---

<section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-[#F0F4F8] section-mountains" id="ueber-mich" aria-label="Über mich">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start">

      <!-- Left: Terminal / Code-Block -->
      <div>
        <div class="terminal-block">
          <div class="terminal-header">
            <span class="terminal-dot bg-[#EF4444]"></span>
            <span class="terminal-dot bg-[#F59E0B]"></span>
            <span class="terminal-dot bg-[#10B981]"></span>
            <span class="ml-3 text-xs text-[#64748B] font-mono">terminal — bash</span>
          </div>
          <div class="terminal-body">
            <div class="terminal-line"><span class="terminal-prompt">$</span> cat über-mich.txt</div>
            <div class="terminal-line terminal-output"><span class="terminal-key">&gt; Name:</span> <span class="terminal-value">Philipp Schlemmer</span></div>
            <div class="terminal-line terminal-output"><span class="terminal-key">&gt; Standort:</span> <span class="terminal-value">Gleisdorf, Steiermark</span></div>
            <div class="terminal-line terminal-output"><span class="terminal-key">&gt; Erfahrung:</span> <span class="terminal-value">15+ Jahre Webentwicklung</span></div>
            <div class="terminal-line terminal-output"><span class="terminal-key">&gt; Fokus:</span> <span class="terminal-value">DSGVO, Performance, GEO</span></div>
            <div class="terminal-line terminal-output"><span class="terminal-key">&gt; Tools:</span> <span class="terminal-value">Astro, Drupal, Tailwind, SEO</span></div>
            <div class="terminal-line"><span class="terminal-prompt">$</span> <span class="terminal-cursor">_</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Text + Stats -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-[#0F172A] mb-6" style="font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif;">
          Persönliche Betreuung<br />
          <span class="text-[#4D7CFF]">statt Callcenter.</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="text-[#475569] leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Kein Ticket-System. Keine Chatbots. Nur ein Mensch, der Ihr Projekt kennt.
        </p>

        <p class="text-[#475569] leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Ich bin Philipp — Webentwickler aus Leidenschaft. Seit über 15 Jahren baue ich Websites, die nicht nur gut aussehen, sondern auch funktionieren. Mein Fokus liegt auf DSGVO-konformen, performanten Lösungen für kleine und mittlere Unternehmen in Österreich.
        </p>

        <p class="text-[#475569] leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Keine versteckten Kosten. Keine Lock-in-Verträge. Nur ehrliche Beratung und handgemachte Qualität — persönlich betreut von der ersten Idee bis zum Launch und darüber hinaus.
        </p>

        <!-- 3 Stats -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <div class="stat-card">
            <p class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#4D7CFF]" style="font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif;">15+</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-[#64748B] mt-1">Jahre</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <p class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#4D7CFF]" style="font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif;">50+</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-[#64748B] mt-1">Projekte</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <p class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#4D7CFF]" style="font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif;">100%</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-[#64748B] mt-1">DSGVO</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Terminal Block */
  .terminal-block {
    background: #0F172A;
    border-radius: 14px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid #1E293B;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px -8px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.2);
  }
  .terminal-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    background: #1E293B;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #334155;
  }
  .terminal-dot {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-right: 6px;
  }
  .terminal-body {
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    font-family: 'Courier New', 'SF Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: #CBD5E1;
  }
  .terminal-prompt {
    color: #4D7CFF;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
  }
  .terminal-cursor {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 8px;
    height: 1.1em;
    background: #4D7CFF;
    animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
    vertical-align: text-bottom;
  }
  @keyframes blink {
    50% { opacity: 0; }
  }
  .terminal-key {
    color: #22D3EE;
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
  }
  .terminal-value {
    color: #E2E8F0;
  }

  /* Stat Cards */
  .stat-card {
    background: #FFFFFF;
    border: 1px solid #E2E8F0;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.25rem 0.75rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }
  .stat-card:hover {
    border-color: #4D7CFF;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px -4px rgba(77, 124, 255, 0.12);
  }
</style>
